name: Jumping Jack (itch) (SreehariSandeep)
description:
This is an easy and entertainable video game for kids made by an 12 year old. Its just made for the entertainment of small kids. So download it and have fun.

Background Music by Cleyton Kauffman - https://soundcloud.com/cleytonkauffman

Jumping Sound By Boing Raw Copyright 2005 cfork Boing Jump Copyright 2012 Iwan Gabovitch 

  Snake Image By Snake icons created by Freepik - Flaticon

The controls are pretty easy

Left Arrow To Move Left.

Right Arrow To Move Right.

Up Arrow To Jump.
